{"id":58580,"date":"2024-08-15T17:19:00","date_gmt":"2024-08-15T11:49:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=58580"},"modified":"2024-08-21T17:47:18","modified_gmt":"2024-08-21T12:17:18","slug":"small-almirah-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/small-almirah-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Stunning Small Almirah Design Ideas to Elevate Your Home Interiors"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A small almirah design is a significant part of your bedroom interiors as it keeps your bedroom more organised and exudes charm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A small almirah design is an integral fixture of almost all Indian households. Every bedroom has at least one or two almirahs to store expensive clothes, jewellery, personal valuables, and other accessories. This style can also be built or installed in a kitchen to display <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/choosing-appliances-for-your-kitchen\/\">kitchen appliances<\/a>, organise crockery and grocery items, and more.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s a low down on the most trending small almirah design ideas for modern homeowners. Get inspired and make the best pick.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Almirah for Kids Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This small off-white matte-finish laminate <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/kids-bedroom-interiors\/kids-wardrobe-designs\/\">almirah for the kid\u2019s room<\/a> almost merges with the white-brick accent wall and making the whole structure look cohesive. It has a unique door design with long pull handles, which creates visual interest. The wooden study table, wall art, and grey-cushioned chair perfectly contrast the overall theme of the space.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small Almirah design for kids bedroom which looks quite quirky\" class=\"wp-image-58585\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173615\/kids-small-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A quirky cupboard adds depth to the room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Wall Almirah Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This small iron almirah design features a hinged double door with a mirror on one side. The mirror makes it easier for the person to groom themselves without going to a separate area, thereby saving effort and time. It also reflects light, which makes the bedroom look larger and brighter. The combination of olive green and white colour of the painted almirah looks quite soothing to the eye.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small wall Almirah design which utilises the unused corner\" class=\"wp-image-58584\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173605\/small-wall-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The freestanding almirah utilises the unused corner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Home interiors that promise an instant upgrade!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/11122626\/home-interiors-that-promise-instant-upgrade.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Size Almirah for the Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a deep niche in your kitchen that you plan to use but don&#8217;t know how to, then this small metal almirah design will work wonders for you. It is so sleek it can accommodate a fridge beside it conveniently. The semi-gloss finish of the cupboard doors accentuates the overall look and feel of the space and makes it easier for you to store the essentials and access them.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small metal Almirah design for the kitchen which works wonder\" class=\"wp-image-58583\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173556\/kitchen-small-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add a green plant to bring nature indoors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Plastic Almirah<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are creative and love experimenting with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interiors<\/a>, you can choose this small plastic-doored wall almirah design. The half-sized cupboard is suspended from the ceiling and supported by the back wall to give it a designer effect. Inside it, you can accommodate clothes and non-precious grooming essentials for much-needed privacy.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small plastic Almirah design which saves the floor space\" class=\"wp-image-58582\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173546\/small-plastic-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Save floor space with this unique design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Almirah: Small Wonders<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This dark brown full-length wooden small almirah with carved door knobs gives a very rustic and traditional vibe to the bedroom area. It complements the light woodwork as a sideboard, attached study table, and lofts and anchors all the elements in the space together. The sunburst mirror and the comfy armchair serve as the cherry on the cake as they add a sense of luxury and sophistication to the entire theme of the room.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small wooden Almirah design in dark brown with carved door knobs\" class=\"wp-image-58581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/21173536\/small-wooden-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sturdy cupboard makes life easy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Explore multi functional, aesthetic and well-designed home interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/10181054\/Explore-multi-functional-aesthetic-and-well-designed-home-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wrapping Up<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Opting for a small almirah design will provide you with immense design flexibility and functionality in your home. So, if you\u2019re considering purchasing or building one for your living space, try your hands at<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"> DesignCafe<\/a>. Our team of interior designers is just a call\/email away, and they can guide you in choosing the perfect small almirah design from among the plethora of options available to suit your every need.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Small Almirah Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What door options are suitable for small almirahs to provide easy access &amp; save space?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Sliding Doors (contemporary look | slide horizontally on a tracking mechanism | ideal for small spaces | more practical as it doesn\u2019t obstruct traffic flow around it | provides adequate storage space).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Swing Doors (traditional or classic look | operate on hinges fixed to one side of the almirah and swing open | can be customised as single or double door | ideal for large spaces).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Folding Doors (highly versatile | mechanism of multiple panels that fold in on themselves when opened | ideal for small and large spaces).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mirrored Doors (can be customised as hinged or sliding | add a sense of space in the room via light reflection | can be installed as a whole panel or integrated with other materials like metal or wood | extremely practical as they eliminate the need for a separate dressing mirror).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Other small almirah door design options are also available.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do you customise the interior layout of a small almirah to maximise storage efficiency &amp; retain personal style?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Create a cohesive look for your small almirah design interiors that blends well with the existing decor of the bedroom or any other relevant space by experimenting with the power of textures and colours.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Clear the visual clutter by properly \u2018file folding\u2019 your clothes, organising your accessories, and disposing unused boxes or ill-fitting garments. Devise an almirah cleaning ritual every six months.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integrate smart storage solutions into the small almirah interiors, such as hanging rods, multi-tier hangers, built-in drawers\/compartments, shoe racks, storage bins\/under-shelf baskets, and adjustable regular\/corner shelves.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Showcase the small-size almirah with the perfect lighting choices, such as inbuilt cabinet lighting, LED strip lights, or fashionable pendant lights that make finding your favourite outfits easy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the Vastu tips for a small almirah design in your bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Position your small almirah design in the South-West direction and face it in the East\/North direction.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Don\u2019t put a mirror in the south-west direction of the small almirah design as it reflects negative energies.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A small almirah design should be painted in neutral or light colours, such as pastels, cream, beige, and white.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Place your small almirah with a locker for cash or other valuables in the North and ensure that it has a single door.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Opt for a wooden or iron almirah design as it is more sustainable, eye-pleasing and stores positive vibes.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input 